author: Wintergatan
description:
We started a new collaboration project on the Marble Machine Engineering Server.
If you want to contribute with CAD design, you are more than welcome to the server here:
https://discord.gg/CjkA5cNK

Thank you to everyone who has already submitted designs, I am truly grateful for everyone's efforts especially at this time. This project has already taught me a lot about how to collaborate with The Wintergatan Internet Team on a large scale. Very promising dress rehearsal ahead of the future Marble Machine Collaborations :)

Hannes has been on to me about dropping the ball on my daughters name though, she isn't going to be named Marbelle despite all Hannes efforts ;)

Thank you Elisabeth for always being there for me and for bringing our daughter to the world.

/Martin

Support Wintergatan:
- Patreon ► https://patreon.com/Wintergatan
- Youtube membership ► https://bit.ly/4cQVM7C

Video edited By Martin and Hannes from the Trainerds YouTube Channel:
